## +-------------------------------------------------------------------------+
## | Does an observation have data within the chart's rolling window?         |
## |                                                                          |
## | Charts on the current page plot $custom_time_delta (a ~24h window that   |
## | crosses midnight), so visibility must be decided against that span, NOT  |
## | $day (midnight->now). Otherwise a calm/empty morning hides a chart that  |
## | still has data from earlier in the window (e.g. yesterday evening).      |
## | Value-cards keep using $day on purpose: they show today's stats.         |
## +-------------------------------------------------------------------------+
